{"tid":1768392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕送暖行動 大家一齊寄聖誕卡俾施永青","createTime":"2019-12-04T04:34:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T08:29:42.000Z","uid":281492,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"430990b4edaba4f34cb3aeba9bdc7e4723b5fc5d","tid":1768392,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:34:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n施先生細個無聖誕卡，我哋係時候要俾啲溫暖佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>地址：</strong><br />\n<strong>施永青基金</strong><br />\n地址：香港中環皇后大道中18號新世界大廈1座22樓 行政總裁施永青<br />\n<strong>中原地產</strong><br />\n香港中環皇后大道中十八號新世界大廈1座5樓 中原集團主席施永青<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">聲明：<br />\n雖然本人叫施施，但本人與施永青絕無半點關係。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你個閪啦施永青</strong></span><br />\n施永青 : 黃店貼紙效果一如黑社會過年要商戶買桔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1766856</a></span>"},{"pid":"7c7995b27eb41ace2ce1434302de6d6864ffa300","tid":1768392,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"係寫都寫比義士先"},{"pid":"d1c00503c56434b2479035fa9abe3f811560d617","tid":1768392,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c7995b27eb41ace2ce1434302de6d6864ffa300","tid":1768392,"uid":70745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"係寫都寫比義士先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"寫咗啦！<br />\n手痕想寫多封俾施先生啫"},{"pid":"3773297d07b39495cfc63c47ef97bc03ba453881","tid":1768392,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"(twitter要人）意大利議會 外務委員會 支持香港, 要求歐盟調查香港警暴<br />\n<a href=\"https